title: x/mobile/gobind: duplicate word in error messages
body:
/Users/jra/bin/gomobile: type github.com/kellydunn/golang-geo.Point not defined in package package marshrutme ("github.com/jeffallen/marshrutme")

"in package package" is because the error is "in package %s", with %s filled by a types.Package, which has a String() method that puts "package" on the front.

There are several occurrences of "in package" in gengo.go that probably all need fixing.
